00:28:01.284 --> 00:28:02.123
Kong Hou.

00:28:02.563 --> 00:28:04.004
What do you want?

00:28:04.204 --> 00:28:05.724
As long as the Yunhua Sect

00:28:05.724 --> 00:28:06.803
follows my order

00:28:07.004 --> 00:28:08.524
and surrenders ten people,

00:28:08.883 --> 00:28:09.803
naturally,

00:28:09.803 --> 00:28:11.168
I'll guarantee your safety.

00:28:11.803 --> 00:28:13.152
Otherwise,

00:28:14.563 --> 00:28:16.160
I'm not sure

00:28:16.883 --> 00:28:18.284
what I'll do.

00:28:18.284 --> 00:28:19.643
Kong Hou.

00:28:20.363 --> 00:28:21.883
Wake up.

00:28:22.004 --> 00:28:22.924
- (Master, don't worry.)
- Look

00:28:22.924 --> 00:28:23.872
- (I won't hurt them.)
- at them.

00:28:23.968 --> 00:28:24.665
They are

00:28:24.724 --> 00:28:27.163
- (This is a stalling tactic.)
- your fellow disciples...

00:28:27.163 --> 00:28:28.004
Silence.

00:28:38.244 --> 00:28:39.284
I'll go with you.

00:28:40.684 --> 00:28:41.536
Ling Hui.

00:28:42.240 --> 00:28:43.323
Me too.

00:28:43.643 --> 00:28:44.563
Excellent.

00:28:45.163 --> 00:28:47.843
The wise ones know when to yield.

00:28:48.524 --> 00:28:50.083
You saved me the trouble.

00:28:50.163 --> 00:28:51.083
Guards.

00:28:52.083 --> 00:28:54.843
Take them away.

00:28:56.044 --> 00:28:56.960
Kong Hou.

00:28:57.724 --> 00:28:58.688
Kong Hou.

00:28:59.403 --> 00:29:00.284
Kong Hou.

00:29:15.924 --> 00:29:18.284
What Gu parasite

00:29:18.284 --> 00:29:20.192
did Jiusu plant in me?

00:29:20.524 --> 00:29:21.524
I've read so many books

00:29:21.524 --> 00:29:23.284
on the Gu parasites,

00:29:23.444 --> 00:29:25.323
but couldn't find any clues.

00:29:26.724 --> 00:29:28.684
Young Master, you should rest.

00:29:28.803 --> 00:29:29.964
Xiao Pei.

00:29:30.163 --> 00:29:31.563
When will Kong Hou come?

00:29:32.363 --> 00:29:34.204
I don't know where Her Eminence is.

00:29:34.363 --> 00:29:35.964
Have some spiritual fruits first.

00:29:41.764 --> 00:29:42.764
Please wait.

00:29:44.803 --> 00:29:46.444
What else do you need?

00:29:46.603 --> 00:29:48.444
There's something you should know.

00:29:48.724 --> 00:29:51.563
I regulated energy
with Kong Hou some days ago.

00:29:51.684 --> 00:29:53.403
Her energy flow was chaotic

00:29:53.924 --> 00:29:55.123
and her blood flow reversed.

00:29:55.244 --> 00:29:56.603
She needs treatment,

00:29:57.603 --> 00:29:58.944
or she might be in trouble.

00:29:59.484 --> 00:30:00.843
How did that happen?

00:30:00.843 --> 00:30:02.764
W-What should I do?

00:30:04.163 --> 00:30:05.204
Please

00:30:05.444 --> 00:30:07.284
keep me informed

00:30:07.323 --> 00:30:08.964
if anything happens.

00:30:09.924 --> 00:30:10.643
Alright.

00:30:12.204 --> 00:30:13.123
Young Master,

00:30:13.323 --> 00:30:14.684
you seem to care deeply

00:30:14.684 --> 00:30:16.403
about Her Eminence.

00:30:16.803 --> 00:30:18.204
You love her, don't you?

00:30:20.484 --> 00:30:21.123
Yes.

00:30:22.123 --> 00:30:23.724
She's the love of my life.

00:30:23.843 --> 00:30:24.724
How nice.

00:30:25.284 --> 00:30:26.284
Her Eminence

00:30:26.323 --> 00:30:27.403
is suffering.

00:30:27.643 --> 00:30:29.204
Each day weighs on her spirit.

00:30:29.284 --> 00:30:30.363
Lord Jiusu forces her

00:30:30.363 --> 00:30:31.764
to cultivate every day.

00:30:32.204 --> 00:30:33.924
